<span class="displaytext"><h4>prominent (PARTY NAME) leaders endorse (candidate last) for president</h4> <p><b>austin, texas</b> – as senator (candidate full) visits austin today to attend a "small change for big change" grassroots fundraiser, the (candidate full) for president campaign announced that 20 texas (PARTY NAME) are endorsing (candidate last) for president, including several members of the texas state house of representatives. these (PARTY NAME) join congresswoman eddie bernice johnson, congressman charlie gonzalez, and former congressman and 2006 (PARTY NAME) gubernatorial nominee chris bell, all of whom have previously announced their support for senator (candidate last). </p><p>former congressman max sandlin said, "(candidate full) is a rare candidate - he has both the courage to stand up for the core values we believe in as (PARTY NAME), and the ability to compete everywhere in the country, including here in texas." </p><p>"(candidate full) has spent his life speaking out for those without a voice," said texas house (PARTY NAME) leader jim dunnam. "i am proud to support a (PARTY NAME) who will fight for working americans and bring about real change in our country." </p><p>"we need a (PARTY NAME) in the white house in 2008 to fix the damage done by the bush administration and put our country back on track," said state representative garnet coleman. "(candidate full) is the best (PARTY NAME) to take back the white house and restore america to its place of leadership." </p><p>"(candidate full) is a true leader who can bring together all americans," said state representative trey martinez fischer. "he has bold plans to transform our country—plans to end the war in iraq, guarantee health care for every american, halt global warming and strengthen the middle class." </p><p>"i encourage all texans to join me in supporting a great (PARTY NAME), a great husband, great father, and most of all a great american—(candidate full) for president," said charles soecht